Q8. Shifting Elements in Array  ?
Required for inserting/deleting in middle.
inserting :
-----------
int[] arr = new int[6];
int size = 3;
int index = 1;
int value = 99;

for (int i = size; i > index; i--) {
    arr[i] = arr[i - 1];  // Shift right
}
arr[index] = value;
size++;

deleting:
---------
Delete with Shift ?
int index = 1;

for (int i = index; i < size - 1; i++) {
    arr[i] = arr[i + 1];  // Shift left
}
size--;




